@model CourseDetailViewModel
<section class="course-info">
    <div class="row">
       <div class="col-md-9">
          <h1>@Model.Title</h1>
       </div>
       <div class="col-md-3 d-flex align-items-end">
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg btn"> Iscriviti </a>
       </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-9">
            <p>@Model.Description</p>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quisquam accusamus fuga quidem obcaecati nesciunt! Quidem sapiente placeat, ratione ea corrupti illo iure praesentium expedita suscipit quos. Sunt culpa tempore voluptate.</p>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Id quia cumque tempore commodi fugiat. Saepe magnam asperiores aut aliquam dolorum illum itaque dolore perferendis aspernatur maxime doloribus, quas repellat nisi!</p>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Eum incidunt ea dolore sit repellat excepturi quas, odit ipsa deleniti consectetur esse quam corrupti doloribus. Quidem hic consequuntur quas est aut!</p>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Amet perspiciatis adipisci voluptas odit fugit nisi, voluptatibus corporis, tempora natus quod quam velit, consectetur cum eligendi ullam commodi officiis nostrum dolore?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <aside>
                <author>@Model.Author </author>
                <div class="rating" title="@Model.Rating">
                    @for(int i = 1; i <= 5; i++)
                    {
                        if(Model.Rating >= i)
                        {
                            <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                        }
                        else if(Model.Rating > i - 1)
                        {
                            <i class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            <i class="far fa-star"></i>
                        }
                    }
                </div>
                <div class="price">
                    @Model.CurrentPrice
                    @if(!Model.CurrentPrice.Equals(Model.FullPrice))
                    {
                        <br><s>@Model.FullPrice</s>
                    }
                </div>    
                <img src="@Model.ImagePath" class="img-fl">   
            </aside>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="course-lessons">
    <h2>Lezioni (@Model.Lessons.Count)</h2>
    @foreach(var lesson in Model.Lessons)
    {
        <hr>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-9 d-flex align-items-center">
                <a href="#">@lesson.Title</a>
            </div> 
            <div class="col-md-3 d-flex align-items-center lesson-duration">
            <i class="far fa-clock"></i><time>@lesson.Duration.ToString("m'm 's's'")</time>
            </div>
        </div>
    }
    <hr>
    <div class="row course-duration">
        <div class="col-md-9 d-flex align-items-center">
            Totale
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 d-flex align-items-center">
            <i class="far fa-clock"></i><time>@Model.TotalCourseDuration.ToString("m'm 's's'")</time>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>
  